│          (ncasc) (csrc)\n*         └── M12 ──┘                  │   M1 drain\n*           (mirror)                   │\n*                                      │\n*   VDD ──┬── M4  ──┬── mid_n ── M6 ──┬── vout ──── M8 ── M10 ── VSS\n*         │ (fold)  │        (pcasc)   │          (ncasc) (csrc)\n*         └── M13 ──┘                  │   M2 drain\n*           (mirror)                   │\n*\n*   M11 (tail) connects M1/M2 sources to VSS\n*\n* M12/M13 are parallel PMOS current mirrors alongside M3/M4.\n* Both feed into the cascode (M5/M6), preserving output impedance.\n* ============================================================\n\n* Parameterized device sizes for reusability\n.param W1  = 10u   L1  = 1.0u  nf1  = 2\n.param W2  = 10u   L2  = 1.0u  nf2  = 2\n.param W3  =  8u   L3  = 1.0u  nf3  = 2\n.param W4  =  8u   L4  = 1.0u  nf4  = 2\n.param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2\n.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 0.5u  nf6  = 2\n.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 0.5u  nf7  = 2\n.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 0.5u  nf8  = 2\n.param W9  =  4u   L9  = 2.0u  nf9  = 1\n.param W10 =  4u   L10 = 2.0u  nf10 = 1\n.param W11 =  4u   L11 = 4.0u  nf11 = 1\n.param W12 =  8u   L12 = 2.0u  nf12 = 1\n.param W13 =  8u   L13 = 2.0u  nf13 = 1\n\n.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n\n* --- Input Differential Pair ---\nXM1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W={W1} L={L1} nf={nf1}\nXM2 vout   vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W={W2} L={L2} nf={nf2}\n\n* --- Tail Current Source ---\nXM11 tail vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8 W={W11} L={L11} nf={nf11}\n\n* --- PMOS Fold Transistors (current sources from VDD) ---\nXM3 mid_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W={W3} L={L3} nf={nf3}\nXM4 mid_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W={W4} L={L4} nf={nf4}\n\n* --- PMOS Bias Mirror Transistors (parallel with M3/M4) ---\nXM12 mid_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W={W12} L={L12} nf={nf12}\nXM13 mid_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8 W={W13} L={L13} nf={nf13}\n\n* --- PM