{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01McA5rayVg6ZTh4D5qxgAxm","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_015KDE3AtuzzrfoMiUjWQCfM","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_op.spice","content":"* ============================================================\n* TB07: Operating Point Verification — VibroSense OTA\n* ============================================================\n\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\n.param vdd_val = 1.8\n.param ibias_val = 500n\n.param vcm_val = 0.9\n\n* Supply\nVdd vdd 0 dc {vdd_val}\nVss vss 0 dc 0\n\n* Bias generation for Vbn: diode-connected NMOS matching M11 (W=4u, L=4u)\nMbn vbn vbn 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=4u nf=1\nIbias vdd vbn dc {ibias_val}\n\n* Vbcn: NMOS cascode bias\n* Diode-connected cascode + current source mirror generates proper Vbcn\nMbcn vbcn vbcn bcn_src 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=0.5u nf=2\nMbcn_src bcn_src vbn 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=2u nf=1\nIbcn vdd vbcn dc {ibias_val}\n\n* Vbp: PMOS bias — diode-connected PMOS matching M3 (W=8u, L=1u)\nMbp vbp vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\nIbp vbp 0 dc 500n\n\n* Vbcp: PMOS cascode bias\n* Diode-connected PMOS cascode\nMbcp vbcp vbcp bcp_src vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=0.5u nf=2\nMbcp_src bcp_src vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\nIbcp vbcp 0 dc 500n\n\n* Input bias at common-mode\nVinp vinp 0 dc {vcm_val}\nVinn vinn 0 dc {vcm_val}\n\n* Instantiate OTA\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\n\n* Load capacitor\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.op\n.save all\n\n.control\n  run\n\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"======================================================\"\n  echo \"  OPERATING POINT — VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA\"\n  echo \"======================================================\"\n\n  echo \"--- Bias Voltages ---\"\n  print v(vbn) v(vbcn) v(vbp) v(vbcp) v(vout)\n\n  echo \"--- M1 (NMOS input +) W=10u L=1u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m1[id] @m.xota.m1[vgs] @m.xota.m1[vth] @m.xota.m1[vds] @m.xota.m1[vdsat] @m.xota.m1[gm] @m.xota.m1[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M2 (NMOS input -) W=10u L=1u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m2[id] @m.xota.m2[vgs] @m.xota.m2[vth] @m.xota.m2[vds] @m.xota.m2[vdsat] @m.xota.m2[gm] @m.xota.m2[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M3 (PMOS fold +) W=8u L=1u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m3[id] @m.xota.m3[vgs] @m.xota.m3[vth] @m.xota.m3[vds] @m.xota.m3[vdsat] @m.xota.m3[gm] @m.xota.m3[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M4 (PMOS fold -) W=8u L=1u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m4[id] @m.xota.m4[vgs] @m.xota.m4[vth] @m.xota.m4[vds] @m.xota.m4[vdsat] @m.xota.m4[gm] @m.xota.m4[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M5 (PMOS cascode +) W=8u L=0.5u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m5[id] @m.xota.m5[vgs] @m.xota.m5[vth] @m.xota.m5[vds] @m.xota.m5[vdsat] @m.xota.m5[gm] @m.xota.m5[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M6 (PMOS cascode -) W=8u L=0.5u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m6[id] @m.xota.m6[vgs] @m.xota.m6[vth] @m.xota.m6[vds] @m.xota.m6[vdsat] @m.xota.m6[gm] @m.xota.m6[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M7 (NMOS cascode +) W=4u L=0.5u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m7[id] @m.xota.m7[vgs] @m.xota.m7[vth] @m.xota.m7[vds] @m.xota.m7[vdsat] @m.xota.m7[gm] @m.xota.m7[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M8 (NMOS cascode -) W=4u L=0.5u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m8[id] @m.xota.m8[vgs] @m.xota.m8[vth] @m.xota.m8[vds] @m.xota.m8[vdsat] @m.xota.m8[gm] @m.xota.m8[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M9 (NMOS current src +) W=4u L=2u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m9[id] @m.xota.m9[vgs] @m.xota.m9[vth] @m.xota.m9[vds] @m.xota.m9[vdsat] @m.xota.m9[gm] @m.xota.m9[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M10 (NMOS current src -) W=4u L=2u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m10[id] @m.xota.m10[vgs] @m.xota.m10[vth] @m.xota.m10[vds] @m.xota.m10[vdsat] @m.xota.m10[gm] @m.xota.m10[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M11 (NMOS tail) W=4u L=4u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m11[id] @m.xota.m11[vgs] @m.xota.m11[vth] @m.xota.m11[vds] @m.xota.m11[vdsat] @m.xota.m11[gm] @m.xota.m11[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M12 (PMOS