{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01VhNgN2BuYKehV2sNaMTcHH","type":"tool_result","content":"The file /home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice has been updated successfully."}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"5449c6a3-9768-4805-ab18-a43181da88e5","timestamp":"2026-03-22T22:32:01.887Z","tool_use_result":{"filePath":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/ota_foldcasc.spice","oldString":".param W9  =  4u   L9  = 2.0u  nf9  = 1\n.param W10 =  4u   L10 = 2.0u  nf10 = 1","newString":".param W9  =  2u   L9  = 4.0u  nf9  = 1\n.param W10 =  2u   L10 = 4.0u  nf10 = 1","originalFile":"* ============================================================\n* VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA — SKY130A\n* ============================================================\n* Subcircuit: ota_foldcasc\n* Uses raw BSIM4 model names (M-prefix, no subcircuit wrapper)\n* ============================================================\n\n* Parameterized device sizes for reusability\n.param W1  = 10u   L1  = 1.0u  nf1  = 2\n.param W2  = 10u   L2  = 1.0u  nf2  = 2\n.param W3  =  8u   L3  = 1.0u  nf3  = 2\n.param W4  =  8u   L4  = 1.0u  nf4  = 2\n.param W5  =  8u   L5  = 0.5u  nf5  = 2\n.param W6  =  8u   L6  = 0.5u  nf6  = 2\n.param W7  =  4u   L7  = 0.5u  nf7  = 2\n.param W8  =  4u   L8  = 0.5u  nf8  = 2\n.param W9  =  4u   L9  = 2.0u  nf9  = 1\n.param W10 =  4u   L10 = 2.0u  nf10 = 1\n.param W11 =  4u   L11 = 4.0u  nf11 = 1\n.param W12 =  8u   L12 = 2.0u  nf12 = 1\n.param W13 =  8u   L13 = 2.0u  nf13 = 1\n\n.subckt ota_foldcasc vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp\n\n* --- Input Differential Pair ---\nM1 fold_p vinp tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W1} L={L1} nf={nf1}\nM2 vout   vinn tail vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W2} L={L2} nf={nf2}\n\n* --- Tail Current Source ---\nM11 tail vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W11} L={L11} nf={nf11}\n\n* --- PMOS Fold Transistors (current sources from VDD) ---\nM3  mid_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W3} L={L3} nf={nf3}\nM4  mid_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W4} L={L4} nf={nf4}\n\n* --- PMOS Bias Mirror Transistors (parallel with M3/M4) ---\nM12 mid_p vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W12} L={L12} nf={nf12}\nM13 mid_n vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W13} L={L13} nf={nf13}\n\n* --- PMOS Cascode Transistors ---\nM5  fold_p vbcp mid_p vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W5} L={L5} nf={nf5}\nM6  vout   vbcp mid_n vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W={W6} L={L6} nf={nf6}\n\n* --- NMOS Cascode Transistors ---\nM7  fold_p vbcn src_n7 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W7} L={L7} nf={nf7}\nM8  vout   vbcn src_n8 vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W8} L={L8} nf={nf8}\n\n* --- NMOS Current Source Transistors ---\nM9  src_n7 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W9} L={L9} nf={nf9}\nM10 src_n8 vbn vss vss sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W={W10} L={L10} nf={nf10}\n\n.ends ota_foldcasc\n","structuredPatch":[{"oldStart":14,"oldLines":8,"newStart":14,"newLines":8,"lines":[" .param W6  =  8u   L6  = 0.5u  nf6  = 2"," .param W7  =  4u   L7  = 0.5u  nf7  = 2"," .param W8  =  4u   L8  = 0.5u  nf8  = 2","-.param W9  =  4u   L9  = 2.0u  nf9  = 1","-.param W10 =  4u   L10 = 2.0u  nf10 = 1","+.param W9  =  2u   L9  = 4.0u  nf9  = 1","+.param W10 =  2u   L10 = 4.0u  nf10 = 1"," .param W11 =  4u   L11 = 4.0u  nf11 = 1"," .param W12 =  8u   L12 = 2.0u  nf12 = 1"," .param W13 =  8u   L13 = 2.0u  nf13 = 1"]}],"userModified":false,"replaceAll":false}}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_013Ptr2P8NWSAfK18eCecR8C","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now create a cleaner OP testbench with ideal voltage sources for bias tuning:"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3775,"cache_read_input_tokens":196938,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3775},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"4efcf879-887d-4e1d-a749-5ed0d00b402a"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_013Ptr2P8NWSAfK18eCecR8C","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Mv7UpkjWfFHTJCVHE2tRou","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/tb_ota_op.spice","content":"* ============================================================\n* TB07: Operating Point Verification — VibroSense OTA\n* ============================================================\n\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\n.param vdd_val = 1.8\n.param ibias_val = 500n\n.param vcm_val = 0.9\n\n* Supply\nVdd vdd 0 dc {vdd_val}\nVss vss 0 dc 0\n\n* Bias: diode-connected NMOS for Vbn (matches M11: W=4u L=4u)\nMbn vbn vbn 0 0 sky130_fd_pr__nfet_01v8__model W=4u L=4u nf=1\nIbias vdd vbn dc {ibias_val}\n\n* Cascode biases: ideal voltage sources (tuned for proper operation)\n* Vbcn ~ Vbn + Vth_cascode to keep M9/M10 in sat\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.80\n\n* Vbp: diode-connected PMOS for fold current (W=8u L=1u nf=2, same as M3)\nMbp vbp vbp vdd vdd sky130_fd_pr__pfet_01v8__model W=8u L=1u nf=2\nIbp vbp 0 dc 500n\n\n* Vbcp: ideal voltage source for PMOS cascode bias\n* Need to set so M5/M6 drain (fold_p/vout) sits near mid-rail\n* Vbcp ~ Vbp - Vth_cascode (rough)\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.55\n\n* Input bias at common-mode\nVinp vinp 0 dc {vcm_val}\nVinn vinn 0 dc {vcm_val}\n\n* Instantiate OTA\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\n\n* Load capacitor\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.op\n.save all\n\n.control\n  run\n\n  echo \"\"\n  echo \"======================================================\"\n  echo \"  OPERATING POINT — VibroSense Folded-Cascode OTA\"\n  echo \"======================================================\"\n\n  echo \"--- Bias Voltages ---\"\n  print v(vbn) v(vbcn) v(vbp) v(vbcp) v(vout)\n\n  echo \"--- M1 (NMOS input +) W=10u L=1u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m1[id] @m.xota.m1[vgs] @m.xota.m1[vth] @m.xota.m1[vds] @m.xota.m1[vdsat] @m.xota.m1[gm] @m.xota.m1[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M2 (NMOS input -) W=10u L=1u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m2[id] @m.xota.m2[vgs] @m.xota.m2[vth] @m.xota.m2[vds] @m.xota.m2[vdsat] @m.xota.m2[gm] @m.xota.m2[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M3 (PMOS fold +) W=8u L=1u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m3[id] @m.xota.m3[vgs] @m.xota.m3[vth] @m.xota.m3[vds] @m.xota.m3[vdsat] @m.xota.m3[gm] @m.xota.m3[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M4 (PMOS fold -) W=8u L=1u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m4[id] @m.xota.m4[vgs] @m.xota.m4[vth] @m.xota.m4[vds] @m.xota.m4[vdsat] @m.xota.m4[gm] @m.xota.m4[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M5 (PMOS cascode +) W=8u L=0.5u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m5[id] @m.xota.m5[vgs] @m.xota.m5[vth] @m.xota.m5[vds] @m.xota.m5[vdsat] @m.xota.m5[gm] @m.xota.m5[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M6 (PMOS cascode -) W=8u L=0.5u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m6[id] @m.xota.m6[vgs] @m.xota.m6[vth] @m.xota.m6[vds] @m.xota.m6[vdsat] @m.xota.m6[gm] @m.xota.m6[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M7 (NMOS cascode +) W=4u L=0.5u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m7[id] @m.xota.m7[vgs] @m.xota.m7[vth] @m.xota.m7[vds] @m.xota.m7[vdsat] @m.xota.m7[gm] @m.xota.m7[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M8 (NMOS cascode -) W=4u L=0.5u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m8[id] @m.xota.m8[vgs] @m.xota.m8[vth] @m.xota.m8[vds] @m.xota.m8[vdsat] @m.xota.m8[gm] @m.xota.m8[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M9 (NMOS current src +) W=2u L=4u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m9[id] @m.xota.m9[vgs] @m.xota.m9[vth] @m.xota.m9[vds] @m.xota.m9[vdsat] @m.xota.m9[gm] @m.xota.m9[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M10 (NMOS current src -) W=2u L=4u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m10[id] @m.xota.m10[vgs] @m.xota.m10[vth] @m.xota.m10[vds] @m.xota.m10[vdsat] @m.xota.m10[gm] @m.xota.m10[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M11 (NMOS tail) W=4u L=4u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m11[id] @m.xota.m11[vgs] @m.xota.m11[vth] @m.xota.m11[vds] @m.xota.m11[vdsat] @m.xota.m11[gm] @m.xota.m11[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M12 (PMOS bias mirror +) W=8u L=2u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m12[id] @m.xota.m12[vgs] @m.xota.m12[vth] @m.xota.m12[vds] @m.xota.m12[vdsat] @m.xota.m12[gm] @m.xota.m12[gds]\n\n  echo \"--- M13 (PMOS bias mirror -) W=8u L=2u ---\"\n  print @m.xota.m13[id] @m.xota.m13[vgs] @m.xota.m13[vth] @m.xota.m13[vds] @m.xota.m13[vdsat] @m.xota.m13[gm] @m.xota.m13[gds]\n\n  echo \"======================================================\"\n  quit\n.endc\n\n.end\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3775,"cache_read_input_tokens":196938,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3775},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"502ba969-c32b-45de-92c2-9407aed299fa"}
