{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01Rtr15qc3497ccVeyXuaY84","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01ADGoMV99pEC8TWtX6SyvFs","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/home/ubuntu/analog-ai-chips/vibrosense/01_ota/sweep_bias.spice","content":"* Bias sweep to find optimal operating point\n.lib \"sky130_minimal.lib.spice\" tt\n.include \"ota_foldcasc.spice\"\n\n.param vdd_val = 1.8\n\nVdd vdd 0 dc {vdd_val}\nVss vss 0 dc 0\n\n* All ideal voltage sources for biases\nVbn  vbn  0 dc 0.58\nVbcn vbcn 0 dc 0.80\nVbp  vbp  0 dc 0.83\nVbcp vbcp 0 dc 0.70\n\n* Inputs at common mode\nVinp vinp 0 dc 0.9\nVinn vinn 0 dc 0.9\n\nXota vinp vinn vout vdd vss vbn vbcn vbp vbcp ota_foldcasc\nCL vout 0 10p\n\n.op\n\n.control\n  * Sweep Vbp to find output at mid-rail\n  let vbp_sweep = vector(21)\n  let vout_sweep = vector(21)\n  let im11_sweep = vector(21)\n\n  let idx = 0\n  foreach vbp_val 0.70 0.72 0.74 0.76 0.78 0.80 0.82 0.84 0.86 0.88 0.90 0.92 0.94 0.96 0.98 1.00 1.02 1.04 1.06 1.08 1.10\n    alter Vbp dc = $vbp_val\n    op\n    let vbp_sweep[idx] = $vbp_val\n    let vout_sweep[idx] = v(vout)\n    let im11_sweep[idx] = @m.xota.m11[id]\n    echo \"Vbp=$vbp_val Vout=$&v(vout) M11_Id=$&@m.xota.m11[id] M3_Id=$&@m.xota.m3[id] M9_Id=$&@m.xota.m9[id]\"\n    let idx = idx + 1\n  end\n\n  quit\n.endc\n\n.end\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1017,"cache_read_input_tokens":208129,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1017},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"01e4b3b1-6a11-48e6-b3e7-40758ef8985d","uuid":"c34ef02b-ad9f-4691-b573-53fbf581f28e"}
